item.title: Ron Gallo's PEACEMEAL Review
item.description: Ron Gallo, PEACEMEAL: (March 5, 2021) I’ve been eagerly anticipating this album since the first single, “HIDE (MYSELF BEHIND YOU)” was released. This track’s chorus-drenched guitar and almost-dancebeat are a far cry from Ron’s early, fuzz and scuzz garage work. Of course, a lot has happened since HEAVY META was released. After a few U.S. tours, two E.P.s and a marriage, Ron’s been pretty busy since 2017. But in trading his fuzz pedals for drum machines, what initially appears to be a kitschy sell out is revealed as something… deeper.
